"Out of Office"

July 24, 2017

|

Bangin' Curry Franklin

We want to take the time to sincerely thank everyone who has come by to enjoy our food, your feedback really allows us to continue with our passion and creativity.

 

We will be taking some time off starting July 28th to welcome another new addition to our family. Certainly exciting and we will be making sure to make memories of these precious moments. 

 

Philly you have made this Journey of ours very memorable and this is just the beginning. We are also excited to announce the construction of our new custom food truck! What does that mean? We would like to showcase more of our creativity and less wait times!!

 

 

Please Stay Tuned!
